<p class="cl">I, {{ borrower_name }}, have applied for a loan, or a series of loans, or for other financial accommodations (the “Credit”) with SOUTH RIVER CAPITAL, LLC (“Lender”). I hereby certify that I am engaged in the following type of business: {{ occupation }}. I hereby further certify that the proceeds of the Credit will be used for the following business and commercial purposes and no other: {{ use_of_proceeds }}.</p>
<p class="cl">This sworn statement is given to the Lender to induce Lender to grant the Credit to me as a “business entity”, as referred to in the Code of Maryland Regulations Section COMAR 21.01.02.01(14), under which I can agree with Lender to any rate of interest on the Credit.</p>

<p class="cl">Dated: {{ closing_date }}</p>
